metadata.description: The SVCC Voxel Collection is part of the SandVegasCasinoClub Multiverse and can be used in the Sandbox Game and probably in other Metaverses as well at a later stage. Owning one of our Voxels and using it as your Avatar in TSG will give you a lot of special benefits. For more information check our Twitter & discord: https://linktr.ee/sandvegas
